{"tid":1545481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應承我，同黑警斷絕任何關係，可以嗎？","createTime":"2019-09-06T02:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T02:57:56.000Z","uid":33939,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a5cc20366a491226ea0fbddfe59a34a89a3e3e61","tid":1545481,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:29:43.000Z","msg":"就算本身係親戚朋友都好，老死不相往來，遇然見到面唔使打招呼。<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾藉口話濫權濫捕打人果啲唔係你親友，唔關佢事。警察份工係要有勇氣同正義，但當依家黑警問題咁嚴重，竟然冇所謂嘅白警去拉啲黑警，竟然冇所謂嘅白警走出嚟話要成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n對罪惡選擇視而不見，為人工前途苟延殘喘，其實都係幫兇。尤其係警務人員。應承我，同佢哋斷絕任何關係。用行動同黑警割蓆，全城孤立黑警。<br />\n<br />\n請各位長期於fb/ig轉換為以下頭像，以給黑警壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3GFpbwV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3GFpbwV.jpg&h=b11282b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05761503f56e3bd1dfa85b36e7ffcb762c307162","tid":1545481,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:40:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請長期用上圖作social media頭像，直到有獨立調查委員會並至調查有結果為止</span>"},{"pid":"3f91ea01f4a8acd490a04678bab9387ed5634b43","tid":1545481,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:43:50.000Z","msg":"黑警不是我親友"},{"pid":"8c28ae32ec35d69fb268bfd18d9fec11e892eaa2","tid":1545481,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:44:52.000Z","msg":"黑警不是我親友"},{"pid":"620563f5755ac79f49405b1a48e6fbfeecc9f156","tid":1545481,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:45:36.000Z","msg":"黑警不是我親友"},{"pid":"bb9a669c48e1b9107c5c4ac19a969cb8fa589e27","tid":1545481,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:45:47.000Z","msg":"黑警不是我親友"},{"pid":"b6fec5a466ed9cb985e51b3fe73de63a83fa0c1f","tid":1545481,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:47:58.000Z","msg":"黑警不是我親友"},{"pid":"2d08f43dc4230ca746f609b936d2927177e344aa","tid":1545481,"uid":33939